name: GINO.
description:
This is Gino. I approached him on the corner of Caroline & Lamar St
I asked him if I could take a photo and he just told me sure.
Not sure what compelled me to ask him to write, but I did even though he was short with me, and he agreed.
His writing and explanation was a bit odd, so I cut the conversation off after listening for a bit. He was definitely one of the strangers that stood out the most to me just due to his page.
